          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"streaming-analyse-des-commandes-temps-reel\">Streaming - Analyse des Commandes Temps Reel</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Ce notebook permet de :</span>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Consommer les commandes</strong> depuis Kafka (topic <code>orders_raw</code>)</li>\n<li><strong>Detector les anomalies</strong> en temps reel</li>\n<li><strong>Visualiser les statistiques</strong> des commandes</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"architecture\">Architecture</h2>\n<div class=\"language-scdoc codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>Producer \u2192 Kafka (orders_raw) \u2192 Consumer \u2192 PostgreSQL (streaming.fact_orders)\n                                          \u2198\n                                           Kafka (orders_anomalies) \u2192 Anomaly Consumer\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"configuration\">Configuration</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Verifiez que les services sont demarres :</span>\n<ul>\n<li>Kafka : localhost:9092</li>\n<li>Kafbat UI : <a href=\"http://localhost:8090\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8090</a></li>\n<li>PostgreSQL : localhost:5432</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
